Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.54,Kaho,,0,0,0,, I still have a lot left!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.02,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!!!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:24.19,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ah, please come watch!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:27.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’re from the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:33.01,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’re gonna hold the best performance ever at our Rindou Festival, so we hope you’ll be there!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:45.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Saaa-yaaa-kaaa-chaaan!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:49.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,C’mon, don’t be so shy! Give it everything you’ve got!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:51.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You look reeeally cute!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:27.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:35.36,Kaho,,0,0,0,,When I went with Kozue-senpai to help out at that cafe, the staff told us that we looked really good in these!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:42.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Then I asked if we could borrow those cute uniforms again someday!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:52.58,Kaho,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I figured that since we were gonna be performing live, I want a lot of people to come watch!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:02:01.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I want everyone to see me wearing costumes like these on stage so we can all blossom into smiles!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:09.30,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Please come watch!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.50,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’re from the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:16.21,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’ll definitely be holding a performance!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:20.21,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Thank you very much! I’ll do my best!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.93,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We want to make the Rindou Festival the best thing ever!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.97,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:29.47,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Phew…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh? What’s up, you two?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.39,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ooh, really~!? Thanks!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.59,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But, I don’t really get it.\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:53.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’m not like Sayaka-chan.\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:57.55,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I still don’t really know what’s the point of handing out these flyers!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:05.69,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:28.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.79,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s what you mean.\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:39.81,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I became a school idol because I wanted to blossom!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:46.74,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And that’s why I want to perform at the Rindou Festival, and definitely why I want to perform at Love Live!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:50.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I want to blossom! Right there, on stage! In front of everyone!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:01.54,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ehehe. I don’t know if this is it,\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:07.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,but maybe that was the purpose Sayaka-chan \Nmentioned the student council president had?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.21,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But again, I might be wrong!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.54,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Let’s look for the answer while we hand out these flyers! Yeah!?\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.57,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hurry!!!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.57,Kaho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:08.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Pleeease! Come waaatch!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:11.50,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Kaho-chan, Sayaka-chan, I only have a little more!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:19.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s not it! I meant my battery!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:57.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Have confidence! You’re super cute!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hope to see you there!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:26.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah… but this was a really nice idea, Kaho-chan.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:43.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You were shining super bright, Kaho-chan!\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}What do you mean, Sayaka-chan?\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:57.01,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You want to perform at Love Live! so you can blossom… huh…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.84,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m not sure I have one of those.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:24.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But if the president wants us to look for our own reasons to perform in Love Live!, then…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.43,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Y-yeeah…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:36.69,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,U-Uhhhh…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.90,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Why…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.14,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,why these…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:42.80,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,these…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,B-But, do I really need this sash!?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:08.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You do! Definitely! Everyone needs to see it!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:12.03,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is what we’re deciding to emphasize!?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:14.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,–Ah, yes! Please take this!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:18.24,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s information on the upcoming Hasunosora Rindou Festival!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:47.62,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Y-You sure do commit to things, huh…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Nothing…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.59,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I just thought, you were really…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,No…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:04.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think you’re fine just the way you are now.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.88,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Even back when we first met…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.44,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san’s been saying she wants everyone to watch her so she can blossom…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:23.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It left quite an impression on me.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:12.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Not why the second-years want to perform in Love Live!, but why {\i1}we{\i0} do…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.35,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,O-Okay…!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.75,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Kaho-san!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Rurino-san’s battery…!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
